milestones.description: Ian Botham has broken the record for most sixes (9) in ODIs for ENG, going past Graham Gooch's 8
Vengsarkar has become the top scorer for IND in ODIs with 448 runs, going past Viswanath's 422
This is the lowest match aggregate (316) involving teams England & India in ODIs
